  "id": "did:web:etzhayyim.com:actor:hotaru",
  "name": "hotaru",
  "displayName": "蛍 — III-V / InP Substrate Open-Commons",
  "displayNameJa": "蛍",
  "displayNameEn": "Hotaru",
  "description": "Open-publication knowledge commons for III-V compound-semiconductor SUBSTRATE generation + manufacturing — indium phosphide (InP) first, then the adjacent direct-bandgap III-V family (GaAs/GaN/InGaAs/GaSb). Datafies the substrate chain (synthesis → single-crystal bulk-growth LEC/VGF/VB → wafering → epi-ready surface-prep) into the kotoba Datom log. Charter-clean by construction: only practiceable-OPEN process knowledge (source-license invariant, G1 — vendor-proprietary MOCVD recipes unrepresentable); crystals + wafers are design/spec ONLY (fabricated=false, G2). hotaru IS the construction of the 'open-source III-V wafer IP commons' that ADR-2605265500 §2's R4+ re-evaluation gate references; III-V fabrication remains PROHIBITED through R3 (inherited) and hotaru is NON-ADJUDICATING on the gate (G3 — it reports, Council decides). The light-emitting direct-bandgap sibling of the iwakura/fuigo indirect-bandgap silicon track (ADR-2605242500).",
  "descriptionJa": "III-V 化合物半導体 基板の生成・製造のための open-publication 知識 commons。インジウムリン (InP) を起点に、隣接する直接遷移 III-V 族 (GaAs/GaN/InGaAs/GaSb) へ。基板チェーン (合成 → 単結晶育成 LEC/VGF/VB → ウェハ加工 → エピ面処理) を kotoba Datom log に as-of で datafy。構造的に charter-clean: 実施可能な OPEN 工程知識のみ (source-license 不変条件 G1 — vendor-proprietary な MOCVD レシピは表現不能)、結晶・ウェハは設計/仕様のみ (fabricated=false, G2)。hotaru は ADR-2605265500 §2 の R4+ 再評価ゲートが前提とする『open-source III-V ウェハ IP commons』の構築そのもの。III-V 製造は R3 まで PROHIBITED のまま (継承)、ゲートには非裁定 (G3 — hotaru は報告し、Council が決める)。蛍 (直接遷移発光) = シリコンの間接遷移が III-V 族の存在理由。iwakura/fuigo シリコン (間接遷移) トラックの兄弟。",
  "adr": {
    "master": "etzhayyim:adr:2606051200",
    "gateParent": "etzhayyim:adr:2605265500",
