    "phase": "R0 — 5 cells (all 5 coded state machines; .solve() wrappers still raise at R0) + 6 lexicons + ontology + analyzer (maturity-score + per-material chain-completeness metrics). 53 tests green (25 methods + 28 cells). Design/datafication/simulation only; NO fabrication.",
    "scopeBoundary": "Open-publication III-V/InP substrate commons (生成 + 製造 knowledge) + readiness reporting",
    "exclusions": [
      "III-V fabrication — PROHIBITED through R3 (ADR-2605265500 §2)",
      "vendor-proprietary MOCVD/epitaxy recipes — unrepresentable (G1)",
      "physically grown crystals / manufactured wafers — fabricated=false (G2)",
      "silicon logic/compute ASIC fab — iwakura/fuigo/tsukuru track (ADR-2605242500)",
      "silicon solar PV — himawari (ADR-2606021200)",
      "military / fire-control / weapons-seeker III-V designs (Charter §2(a), N1)",
      "In/Ga sourced without conflict-free/recycled attestation (G4)",
      "deciding or advocating the ADR-2605265500 R4+ gate (G3 — Council Lv7+ only)"
    ]
  },
